{"tid":714722,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《美女廚房》新不如舊？","createTime":"2018-06-23T21:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T03:18:10.000Z","uid":160977,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a474bebfc800c3bf893597ed6c182c7e83769f","tid":714722,"uid":160977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T21:49:29.000Z","msg":"第三輯《美女廚房》出咗街成個星期，網民幾乎一面倒不看好。無他嘅，首兩輯由鄭中基、方力申、梁漢文主持嘅《美女廚房》實在太精彩，笑料一集接一隻，鑊鑊新鮮鑊鑊金，要超越佢真係難度不淺。<br />\n<br />\n珠玉在前，有比較有傷害。舊版《美女廚房》三位主持代表性極高，網民難免將佢哋同《美女廚房》金漆招牌畫上等號絕對理解，而當節目冇咗鄭中基、方力申同梁漢文，短期內收視大減絕對是人之常情。情況就如同睇《超級無敵獎門人》見唔到志偉哥，去麥當勞冇得嗌薯條食一樣，結果都係令人覺得難以接受，部分人甚至寧願選擇不看不吃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2MPCjbc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MPCjbc&d=HcadlA1bA2XoVPK3oCgCFIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=249694ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2MPCjbc</a>"},{"pid":"a2651e0141686ba51d8b04ed6a4d6dae3cca50a4","tid":714722,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T21:50:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ccbecf5e6647f9f9e2b8cc1e3df38d3872a8aea","tid":714722,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T01:54:46.000Z","msg":"無人睇CCTVB"},{"pid":"0c9d398a511a143bb68a2297d6626043d4f079c0","tid":714722,"uid":92477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406b16fbc7ae6b126584f066a9c95a14fa991a47","tid":714722,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:18:10.000Z","msg":"cctvb?! who cares?"}]}